Package: textility
Title: Utility functions for text mining
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Manuel", "Bickel", email = "manuel.bickel@posteo.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Collection of miscellaneous utility functions for text mining, 
             covering, e.g., matrix type conversion, text processing, parallel pos tagging, or calculating topic coherence.
			 Many functions wrap functionality of exisiting packages into customized functions for typical use cases
			 or serve to speed up the functionality by parallelisation (e.g. for pos tagging).
Depends: R (>= 3.4.3)
License:  GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: data.table,
    stringi
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
